`` Scars to Your Beautiful '' is a song by Canadian singer and songwriter Alessia Cara for her debut studio album , Know-It-All -LRB- 2015 -RRB- .
It was released to Top 40 radio on July 26 , 2016 , as the third single from the album .
It peaked at number eight and thus became Alessia Cara 's second top-ten single on US Billboard Hot 100 .
The song was written by Cara , Warren Felder , Coleridge Tillman , and Andrew Wansel , with the production being handled by Felder , Tillman , and Wansel .